folder: Bridge Street & Prospect Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
117-121 Bridge Street, east side, at Prospect Street. The view shows frame buildings at 119-121 Bridge Street; also, 141-149 Prospect, at, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of Bridge Streets.

November 1, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.
